<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forfeo Lab | Excellence Client</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; text-align: center; color: #333; }
        .hero { background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 80px 20px; }
        .auth-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; padding: 50px; background: #f4f4f4; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .card { background: #fff; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 15px; width: 350px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #000; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .btn { padding: 14px; border: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; width: 100%; font-size: 16px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-blue { background: #00aaff; color: white; }
        .btn-blue:hover { background: #0088cc; }
        .btn-black { background: #000; color: white; }
        .btn-black:hover { background: #333; }
        .link-ambassadeur { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; color: #00aaff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Forfeo Lab</h1>
        <p>Optimisez l'expérience client grâce à nos ambassadeurs certifiés.</p>
        <a href="/candidature" class="link-ambassadeur">Devenir Ambassadeur →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="auth-container">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Nouvelle Entreprise</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Créez votre compte pour commander vos premiers audits.</p>
            <form action="/signup-entreprise" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="nom" placeholder="Nom de l'entreprise" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email professionnel" required>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Créer un mot de passe" required>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-blue">Créer mon compte</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Déjà client ?</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Accédez à vos rapports et votre dashboard Forfeo.</p>
            <form action="/login-entreprise" method="POST">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Votre Email" required>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" required>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-black">Se connecter</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/forfy') %>
</body>
</html>
